## HTML5 mini audio sequencer

image::img/simpleui-v04-trix-2019-720x754.png[mini sequencer]

I always wanted to make one of these, so that's what I did over the 2018 holidays.

This is a minimal audio sequencer written in plain javascript using simpleui.

The audio is provided by the standard html5 audio api.

It has no other library dependencies.

